Invocation Name: funny quotes
des:
The hottest, funniest quote collection of all time. An array of 100+ funny meme quotes that will entertain you on a daily basis. Whether you need some entertainment in the morning, or you just fancy laughing then make sure you download Funny Quotes!

Over 100+ funny quotes that get updated regularly. It includes:
“An apple a day keeps anyone away if you throw it hard enough.”
“People say everything happens for a reason. So when I punch you in the face, remember I have a reason.”
“That moment when you spell a word so wrong, that even autocorrect is like: I’ve got nothing man.”

Please use the following example phrases when using Funny Quotes:
“Alexa, please open funny quotes and tell me a funny quote”
“Alexa, launch funny quotes”
“Alexa, play funny quotes”
“Alexa, open funny quotes”

If you know of any funny quotes, get in touch and I will add them!
